      <h1><a href="/tedxnus">TEDxNUS - 9 stories in 18 minutes</a></h1>
      <p class="postdate">Length: <strong>22 minutes.</strong> Date recorded: 2010-10</p>
    </header>
    <p><strong>9 short stories to a TEDx crowd at the National University of Singapore.</strong></p>

<p>
I was asked at the last minute to speak at a TEDx conference the National University of Singapore. I didn't have time to prepare a big 20-minute talk, so I shared nine of my best little 2-minute stories.<br>
<br>
Explanation of the opening minute: the two talks right before me were about evolution and insect penises. I couldn't resist a punchline. ☺
</p>
